
.panel.panel-default
	.panel-heading
		.row
			.col-lg-10
				h3.panel-title {{ctrl.data.id}}. {{ctrl.data.title}} 
			.col-lg-2.pull-right.text-right
				i.fa.fa-pencil-square-o
	.panel-body
		.row.row-centered
			.col-lg-11.col-centered
				h4 Description
				p {{ctrl.data.description}}
		.row.row-centered
			.col-xs-11.col-sm-11.col-md-11.col-lg-12.col-centered
				.well
					fieldset
						.col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-12.col-lg-12
							h4 Information
						.form-group
							label.col-lg-3 Recommender
							.col-xs-9.col-sm-9.col-md-9.col-lg-9
								p {{ctrl.data.recommender}}
						.form-group
							label.col-lg-3 Decision Type
							.col-xs-9.col-sm-9.col-md-9.col-lg-9
								p {{ctrl.data.decisionType}}
						.form-group
							label.col-lg-3 Decision Forum
							.col-xs-9.col-sm-9.col-md-9.col-lg-9
								p {{ctrl.data.decisionForum}}
						.form-group
							label.col-lg-3 Decision Owner
							.col-xs-9.col-sm-9.col-md-9.col-lg-9
								p {{ctrl.data.decisionOwner}}
						.form-group
							label.col-lg-3 Status
							.col-xs-9.col-sm-9.col-md-9.col-lg-9
								p {{ctrl.data.status}}
						.form-group
							label.col-lg-3 Created
							.col-xs-9.col-sm-9.col-md-9.col-lg-9
								p {{ctrl.data.created}}
						.form-group
							label.col-lg-3 Plan Decision Date
							.col-xs-9.col-sm-9.col-md-9.col-lg-9
								p {{ctrl.data.planDecisionDate}}
						.form-group
							label.col-lg-3 Actual Decision Date
							.col-xs-9.col-sm-9.col-md-9.col-lg-9
								p {{ctrl.data.actualDecisionDate}}
					
		.row.equal
			.col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-4.col-lg-4
				.panel.panel-primary
					.panel-heading
						h3.panel-title 
							|Option 1:<br/>
							|Keep functionality 
							|in TSS and manage pick up 
							|transport operations in TSS
					.panel-body
						p  	
							|<i class="fa fa-plus"></i> No disruption of current process for managing distribution services
						p		
							|<i class="fa fa-plus"></i> All current capability for within POL(MAM) will be maintained
						p		
							|<i class="fa fa-plus"></i> Minimum development needs within DDS.
			.col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-4.col-lg-4
				.panel.panel-primary
					.panel-heading
						h3.panel-title 
							|Option 2:<br/>
							|Develop TSS capability in DDS and adopt DDS process
					.panel-body
						p		
							|<i class="fa fa-minus"></i>  Multiple changes need to be performed DSS and in surrounding systems, interfaces (SAP etc.)
			.col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-4.col-lg-4
				.panel.panel-primary
					.panel-heading
						h3.panel-title 
							|Option 3:<br/>
							|Adopt DDS and NO process to current DK process
					.panel-body.text-
						p 		
							|<i class="fa fa-minus"></i> Capability to manage and control transport operations will decreased leading to increase in operational costs
		.row
			.col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-12.col-lg-12
				.alert.alert-success
						|<strong>Recommendation:</strong> {{ctrl.data.recommendation}}

		.row
			.col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-12.col-lg-12
				.alert.alert-success
					|<strong>Decision:</strong> {{ctrl.data.decision}}